WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.200
Since it all starts with the old lady

2
00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:03.866
Then it ends with her

3
00:00:07.766 --> 00:00:09.366
Mr. Lu

4
00:00:09.400 --> 00:00:10.700
You still have the face

5
00:00:10.700 --> 00:00:12.866
Do you know that you have made Mr. Lu miserable?

6
00:00:12.866 --> 00:00:14.366
I'm the one who got hurt

7
00:00:14.466 --> 00:00:16.366
It was miserable by your Lu family

8
00:00:18.566 --> 00:00:19.566
What do you mean?

9
00:00:19.566 --> 00:00:21.133
You didn't keep saying

10
00:00:21.133 --> 00:00:23.200
I am the murderer who killed your father

11
00:00:23.366 --> 00:00:25.000
I'll tell you now

12
00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:26.166
Three years ago.

13
00:00:26.166 --> 00:00:28.900
The real murderer who destroyed your family was your mother

14
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:31.466
My grandmother also failed to treat him in time.

15
00:00:31.466 --> 00:00:32.800
That's why he died

16
00:00:33.333 --> 00:00:34.366
That's not possible.

17
00:00:34.766 --> 00:00:35.966
Shuyuan, are you sick?

18
00:00:35.966 --> 00:00:37.066
Make it up here

19
00:00:39.566 --> 00:00:41.400
Well said because of your mother

20
00:00:41.400 --> 00:00:44.866
That's why my condition is getting worse and worse.

21
00:00:45.300 --> 00:00:47.233
Try moving again.

22
00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:57.066
I just got back from your mother's place

23
00:00:57.200 --> 00:00:57.933
Listen to it yourself

24
00:00:57.933 --> 00:01:00.333
I and Qixiu have now let the Lu family Dongshan again

25
00:01:00.333 --> 00:01:02.833
The truth about the secrets of the past

26
00:01:02.900 --> 00:01:04.600
No one will ever know

27
00:01:04.600 --> 00:01:07.866
Stop! Lu Qi Xiu is usually mean to you

28
00:01:08.066 --> 00:01:09.966
But the pay is not bad

29
00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:11.533
Although the road is dead

30
00:01:11.533 --> 00:01:13.066
He's still your boss

31
00:01:13.066 --> 00:01:14.333
Seek his position

32
00:01:14.333 --> 00:01:15.400
You said it.

33
00:01:15.466 --> 00:01:17.200
You can drive it and deliver it right away.

34
